---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Design in Product - Projects"
activePage: projects
ogTitle: "Projects - Design in Product"
ogDescription: "What happens when a product manager stops just managing products and starts building them — with AI agents as collaborators?"
---

<!-- Hero start -->
<div class="projects-hero">
  <div class="projects-hero__content">
    <h1 class="h1">Building at the Intersection</h1>
    <p class="h2 projects-hero__description">What happens when a product manager stops just managing products and starts building them&mdash;with AI agents as collaborators?</p>
    <p class="projects-hero__subtext">These projects explore the convergence of product management and AI development. From a multi-agent PM assistant to a cuneiform reader, each one tests a different hypothesis about how humans and AI can build together.</p>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- Hero end -->

<!-- Thesis section -->
<div class="projects-thesis">
  <div class="projects-thesis__content">
    <p class="projects-thesis__text">The spectrum below runs from <strong>AI-native systems</strong> (where AI agents are the product) through <strong>AI-assisted experiments</strong> (where AI compressed months of work into days) to <strong>traditional products</strong> (built before the agent era). The contrast tells the story.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Flagship Projects -->
<div class="projects-section">
  <h2 class="projects-section__heading">Flagship Projects</h2>
  <div class="projects-grid projects-grid--flagship">
    {% for project in projects %}
      {% if project.tier == "flagship" %}
      <div class="project-card project-card--flagship">
        <div class="project-card__header">
          <h3 class="project-card__name">{{ project.name }}</h3>
          <span class="project-card__status project-card__status--{{ project.status | lower }}">{{ project.status }}</span>
        </div>
        <p class="project-card__tagline">{{ project.tagline }}</p>
        <p class="project-card__description">{{ project.description }}</p>
        <div class="project-card__tech">
          <span class="project-card__tech-label">Built with:</span>
          <span class="project-card__tech-list">{{ project.techHighlights }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="project-card__categories">
          {% for cat in project.categories %}
          <span class="project-card__category">{{ cat }}</span>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
        <div class="project-card__links">
          <a href="{{ project.url }}" class="btn pink-btn project-card__link" target="_blank">Visit Project</a>
          {% if project.secondaryUrl %}
          <a href="{{ project.secondaryUrl }}" class="btn blue-btn project-card__link" target="_blank">{{ project.secondaryLabel }}</a>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        {% if project.insight %}
        <blockquote class="project-card__insight">
          <p>"{{ project.insight }}"</p>
          {% if project.insightSource %}<cite>— {{ project.insightSource }}</cite>{% endif %}
        </blockquote>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Experiments -->
